(66, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 16, 'Configuration', '<p>Here you can update the Suspicious Words Detector related settings.</p> <p>Here you can place various words, which accepts regular expressions also, to match with your terms and policies. </p> <h4>Common Regular expressions</h4> <dl class="list clearfix"> <dt>Email</dt> <dd>\\w+([-+.]\\w+)*@\\w+([-.]\\w+)*\\.\\w+([-.]\\w+)*([,;]\\s*\\w+([-+.]\\w+)*@\\w+([-.]\\w+)*\\.\\w+([-.]\\w+)*)*</dd> <dt>Phone Number</dt> <dd>(?:+?1)?[-/. ]?[2-9][0-8][0-9][-/. ]?[2-9][0-9]{2}[-/. ]?[0-9]{4}</dd><dd>For reference: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_American_Numbering_Plan#List_of_NANPA_countries_and_territories</dd> </dl>', ''),
