(27, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 25, 'Google PageSpeed', 'Google PageSpeed is also easy to setup through DNS change. This will optimize site''s HTML, JavaScript, Style Sheets and images on the fly. You may not usually need to turn this on as Agriya FPPlatform script is highly optimized already.', 'HighPerformance'),
